## Checklist

Before committing code, verify:

- [ ] File names use kebab-case
- [ ] Component names use PascalCase
- [ ] Imports are grouped and sorted
- [ ] Path aliases used instead of long relative paths
- [ ] Interfaces used instead of types (where appropriate)
- [ ] No enums (use const objects)
- [ ] Environment variables follow naming conventions
- [ ] Git branch name follows convention
- [ ] Commit message follows Conventional Commits
- [ ] Code is organized logically within files
- [ ] Named exports used (unless default required)
